  "summary": "CVE-2025-68615 affecting package net-snmp for versions less than 5.9.5.2-1",
  "details": "net-snmp is a SNMP application library, tools and daemon. Prior to versions 5.9.5 and 5.10.pre2, a specially crafted packet to an net-snmp snmptrapd daemon can cause a buffer overflow and the daemon to crash. This issue has been patched in versions 5.9.5 and 5.10.pre2.",
